## Beta v0.9.6

### Balancing

- Upgrades are a little bit less expensive

### Bugs

- Fixed bug where he drone life could be shown to be less then 0 (e.g. -4) when the drone dies

### Misc

- Improved and re-organized the stat banner in the bottom of the game screen 
- Updated the manual to the new stat banner in the game
- Aligned coloring of the manual to the actual ingame colors

## Files included

- `void-merchants.p8` — PICO-8 standard cart in clear text format
- `void-merchants.p8.png` — PICO-8 cart image
- `void-merchants_linux.zip` — Linux binaries
- `void-merchants_windows.zip` — Windows binaries
- `void-merchants_raspi.zip` — Raspberry Pi binaries
- `void-merchants_osx.zip` — macOS binaries
- `manual.pdf` — Manual for this release
- `LICENSE.txt` — Licensing information